PrecisRe-appointment of Dorothy Davey, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of one year; and designation of the said Dorothy Davey as Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), effective January 1, 1994.
